---

ttw_3way

Map created by Gangstakill
Decals by Enza

---

Objective:

Defensive:
Defend the wall behind your spawn.
If your wall is touched by an enemy you will die.

Offensive:
Touch the wall at the enemies spawn to kill them.

---

Map details:

Fog: Yes
Cover: Yes, mostly in the middle
Size: Small
Deathmatch: No, unless there is a 5 second respawn timer.
Weapons: All, buyzone at spawn.
Players: 18 spawns at each side. making it 36 players maximum.

---
